General.Name: Axolot Solutions Holding AB
General.Description: Axolot Solutions Holding AB (publ), an environmental technology company, provides systems for industrial water purification under the AxoPur and AxoPlus names in Sweden. It offers solutions for industries and waste owners, including effluent purification, waste minimization, process water cleaning for recirculation, energy recovery through water recirculation or floc burning, and material recovery through floc reprocessing. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Helsingborg, Sweden.
